<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;=
Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ligatures:none">From:</span></b><span style=3D"=
font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ligatures:no=
ne"> Grant Metson &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Mets=
