<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello Richard, and A=
ll,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thanks for the reply=
 sent to Tower Insurance below, received on April 9.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have spoken with m=
y colleagues, and we agree that Tower Insurance should provide further detai=
led response to each of the concerns presented within the Prendos Report. As=
 such instructions have been issued
 as follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0in" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 l=
fo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have instructed ASURNZ to provide de=
tailed response with respect to the application of Schedule 1, and provide s=
pecific reference to the relevant clauses
 within the Building Act 2004; and any other relevant legislation which will=
 assist with determination on this issue. I will be able to provide that res=
ponse to you by 4pm on Tuesday April 21.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"=
MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span st=
yle=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have instructed ASURNZ to appoint a CPEng to unde=
rtake an assessment of the unreinforced masonry walls to the perimeter of th=
e basement level of the
 dwelling to ascertain if they have been materially affected by the loss-eve=
nt [fire].<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mar=
gin-left:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I hav=
e instructed ASURNZ to appoint a CPEng to undertake an assessment of the exi=
sting wall bracing elements which are referred to in the Prendos report.
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0=
in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have instruct=
ed ASURNZ to provide drawings of construction details, specification referen=
ces, and other documents which will assist with authenticating
 the aspects of the repairs which are currently within the proposed scope of=
 works. This should provide further clarity and detail for all parties to re=
view.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-l=
eft:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have ins=
tructed ASURNZ to include the replacement of existing thermal insulation to t=
he external basement walls into the proposed scope of work.<o:p></o:p></span=
></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">To complete all the a=
bove we request permission to access the property at
<u>9am on Thursday April 16</u> to allow for assessments and observations to=
 be completed. Noting that item #4 may take a while longer to provide as the=
 drawings will be produced from additional notes &amp; observations taken on=
 the proposed site visit. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Persons who would be=
 present at this site review are as follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0in" type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l2 level1 l=
fo6"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant Metson =E2=80=93 Regional Manage=
r, Structural Assessing, Tower Insurance.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D=
"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo6"><span s=
tyle=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Warwick Banks =E2=80=93 CPEng. KCL Engineering.<o:=
p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;=
mso-list:l2 level1 lfo6"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Stephen Walker =E2=
=80=93 Principal Consultant, ASURNZ.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please relay this re=
quest to Raffaella Del Prete, in order that we receive her permission to vis=
it the property to complete the above, at the date and time prescribed.<o:p>=
</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please confirm at yo=
ur earliest ability, so I can reconfirm this with all parties.<o:p></o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Best Regards,<o:p></=
o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant.<o:p></o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></s=
pan></p>
