<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif">Further to Wynn Williams letter to Tower dated 3 Marc=
h 2026 and our discussion today I confirm our discussion as follows:<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif">This matter has been transferred to me today as my co=
lleague Arna is on family leave and is no longer dealing with claims.<o:p></=
o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif">Tower is concerned that this matter may stagnate and t=
he parties need to reach a go forward position so that the house can be repa=
ired.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif">Tower will request ASURNZ to provide a response to th=
e Prendos report detailing why they don=E2=80=99t believe a Building Consent=
 is necessary.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif">Tower believes the scope of works is appropriate and a=
ccordingly if your client doesn=E2=80=99t believe this to be the case we inv=
ite her to provide a response on the ASURNZ scope
 of works detailing in the scope of works where she doesn=E2=80=99t agree an=
d adding any further items she thinks should be included. It is not Tower=E2=
=80=99s practice to pay for the costs of an Insured=E2=80=99s alternate scop=
e of works as usually these are agreed between the parties
 through discussion.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif">Tower would like to know your client=E2=80=99s prefer=
ence regarding cash settlement or Tower managed repair, noting that ultimate=
ly Tower has final discretion as to which option is
 taken.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif">We look forward to your further response and receipt o=
